OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and bright day with
OL,6,Fplenty of sunshine, the best in the
OL,7,Fmorning with some high cloud arriving
OL,8,Fin the afternoon. Lighter winds, a
OL,9,Fgentle southerly later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will be dry through the
OL,12,Fevening and overnight with
OL,13,Fincreasingly clear skies and a touch
OL,14,Fof grass frost. Becoming breezy around
OL,15,Fthe coast.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FIt will be sunny, breezy and
OL,18,Fwarm, though feeling cool along North
OL,19,FSea coasts. Turning cloudier later
OL,20,Fwith a the odd spot of rain in the
OL,21,Fwest in the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
